OL,6,FVeteran broadcaster Chris Evans has
OL,7,Frevealed he has skin cancer.
OL,9,FOn The Chris Evans Breakfast Show on
OL,10,FVirgin Radio, the 57-year-old said it
OL,11,Fis in the early stages and that he
OL,12,Fwas told the cancer is treatable.
OL,14,FHe told listeners on Monday morning:
OL,15,F"I've just got to talk briefly about
OL,16,Fmy biopsy for the skin cancer issue.
OL,18,F"So, the best news that I got whilst
OL,19,FI was away is that it was a positive
OL,20,Ftest, so I have tested positive for
OL,21,Fskin cancer.
